---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="Learn more about Banavasi - software developer, tech enthusiast, and lifelong learner"
	pubDate={new Date('November 17 2024')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<style>
		.timeline {
			margin: 2rem 0;
		}
		.timeline-item {
			padding-left: 2rem;
			border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
			position: relative;
		}
		.timeline-item::before {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			left: -8px;
			top: 0;
			width: 13px;
			height: 13px;
			border-radius: 50%;
			background: var(--accent);
		}
		.tech-list {
			display: flex;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
			gap: 0.5rem;
			margin: 1rem 0;
		}
		.tech-badge {
			padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
			background: rgb(var(--gray-light));
			border-radius: 6px;
			font-size: 0.9rem;
			color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		}
	</style>

	<h2>Hello, I'm Banavasi! ðŸ‘‹</h2>
	
	<p>
		I'm a passionate software developer with a deep interest in building efficient, scalable, and 
		user-friendly applications. My journey in technology has been driven by curiosity and a constant 
		desire to learn and grow.
	</p>

	<h2>My Background</h2>
	
	<p>
		Throughout my career, I've worked on various projects spanning different domains and technologies. 
		I enjoy tackling complex problems and finding elegant solutions that make a real difference. 
		Whether it's building web applications, optimizing performance, or exploring new frameworks, 
		I'm always eager to expand my skill set.
	</p>

	<h2>What I Do</h2>
	
	<p>
		My expertise includes full-stack development, with a focus on modern web technologies. Here are 
		some of the key areas I work with:
	</p>
	
	<div class="tech-list">
		<span class="tech-badge">JavaScript/TypeScript</span>
		<span class="tech-badge">React & Astro</span>
		<span class="tech-badge">Node.js</span>
		<span class="tech-badge">Cloud Platforms</span>
		<span class="tech-badge">DevOps & CI/CD</span>
		<span class="tech-badge">Git & GitHub</span>
	</div>

	<h2>My Journey</h2>
	
	<div class="timeline">
		<div class="timeline-item">
			<h3>Current Focus</h3>
			<p>Building modern web applications and contributing to open source projects. Focusing on creating 
			efficient, maintainable, and scalable solutions.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="timeline-item">
			<h3>Continuous Learning</h3>
			<p>Exploring new technologies, frameworks, and best practices. Always staying up-to-date with 
			the latest developments in software engineering.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="timeline-item">
			<h3>Community Involvement</h3>
			<p>Sharing knowledge through blog posts, contributing to open source, and helping other developers 
			on their journey.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

	<h2>Beyond Code</h2>
	
	<p>
		When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new technologies, reading tech blogs, or 
		contributing to the developer community. I believe in continuous learning and sharing knowledge 
		with others. This blog is my way of documenting what I learn and helping others on their journey.
	</p>

	<h2>Let's Connect</h2>
	
	<p>
		I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers, collaborating on interesting projects, 
		or simply having a chat about technology. Feel free to reach out through any of the social links 
		on this site. Whether you have questions, suggestions, or just want to say hi, I'd love to hear 
		from you!
	</p>
</Layout>
